  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Space Fuel is a bite-sized arcade shoot 'em up. Pilot your ship through waves of enemy bullets!</strong></h2><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Defeat 4 unique BOSSES:</strong><br>You will encounter 4 BOSSES that you should defeat to get to the next stage. If you beat them all, then you will loop back to the start, but this time BOSSES will be stronger.<br><br></li><li><strong>4 different enemy ships and patterns:</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1361720/extras/76f345107c96800738c1e32052649185.avif?t=1643318394\" width=512 height=128 /></span><br>Fight different enemy ships with unique weapons and attack patterns<br><br></li><li><strong>Try all 5 different power-ups:</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1361720/extras/e1a76c1eb65d89a14928de17d572c740.webp?t=1643318394\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1361720/extras/e1a76c1eb65d89a14928de17d572c740.poster.avif?t=1643318394\" class=\"bb_img\" width=128 height=128 /></picture></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Double shot<br></li><li>Triple shot<br></li><li>Machine gun<br></li><li>Big gun<br></li><li>And even... LASER!<br><br></li><li><strong>Beat your high score:</strong><br>See how far you can go. Meet and defeat BOSS at the end of each stage. Beat your high score.</li></ul></li></ul>",
